# 18-container-registry

Edit \playbook.yml\ and customize \ars/common.yml\ and \inventory.ini\

## Quick Start

1. Update inventory.ini
2. Customize vars/
3. Run: ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini playbook.yml

## Prerequisites

- Ansible 2.9+
- Python 3.6+

## Usage

\\\ash
# Dry-run
ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini playbook.yml --check

# Full execution
ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini playbook.yml

# Verbose
ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini playbook.yml -vvv
